'''艾莉·夏洛克'''（{{lang-en|Allie Sherlock}}，{{bd|2005年|4月7日}}）是一位愛爾蘭歌手、作詞家、吉他手以及街頭藝人。夏洛克2017年6月因翻唱[[紅髮艾德|紅髮艾德]]的歌曲〈{{tsl|en|Supermarket Flowers||Supermarket Flowers}}〉而聞名，2018年夏洛克受邀至《[[艾倫·狄珍妮秀|艾倫·狄珍妮秀]]》<ref name="irishtimes2018">{{cite web|url=https://www.irishtimes.com/culture/music/amazing-12-year-old-irish-busker-wows-the-ellen-show-1.3375116 |title='Amazing': 12-year-old Irish busker wows The Ellen Show |publisher=The Irish Times |date=2018-01-31 |accessdate=2020-04-05}}</ref>。夏洛克經常在[[都柏林|都柏林]][[格拉夫顿街|格拉夫顿街]]表演<ref name="irishtimes2018"/><ref name="examiner2018">{{cite web |url= https://www.irishexaminer.com/breakingnews/lifestyle/culture/cork-teenager-allie-sherlock-is-about-to-the-take-the-next-step-in-her-already-storied-singing-career-892408.html |title=Cork teenager Allie Sherlock is about to the take the next step in her already-storied singing career |last=O'Byrne |first=Ellie |date=2018-12-17 |publisher={{tsl|en|Irish Examiner||Irish Examiner}} |access-date=2020-04-05}}</ref>。

== 生涯==
夏洛克的YouTube頻道建立於2014年<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCGnsRwFS8Xm13lMAeouzT9g |title=Allie Sherlock |website=[[YouTube|YouTube]]}}</ref>。2018年2月，夏洛克在[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]的節目《[[艾倫·狄珍妮秀|艾倫·狄珍妮秀]]》演唱[[愛黛兒|愛黛兒]]的歌曲〈{{tsl|en|Million Years Ago (song)||Million Years Ago}}〉，以及在[[RTÉ_One|RTÉ One]]的節目《{{tsl|en|The Ray D'Arcy Show||The Ray D'Arcy Show}}》演唱[[紅髮艾德|紅髮艾德]]的歌曲〈[[完美無瑕|完美無瑕]]〉<ref>{{cite episode |series=The Ray D'Arcy Show |series-link=The Ray D'Arcy Show |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ELuVYXdSduA |date=2018-02-04 |via=[[YouTube|YouTube]] |title=Allie Sherlock performing 'Perfect' (Ed Sheeran) and interview}}</ref>，夏洛克在同月份與[[共和世代|共和世代]]的主唱[[瑞恩·泰德|瑞恩·泰德]]所擁有的愛國者唱片（Patriot Records）簽下五年合約<ref>{{cite web |title=12-year-old Cork busker scores major deal with US record label| website={{tsl|en|Her.ie||Her.ie}}| date=2018-02-04 |url=https://www.her.ie/entertainment/12-year-old-cork-busker-scores-major-deal-us-record-label-387428 |access-date=2020-04-05}}</ref>。2020年6月，夏洛克在[[愛爾蘭廣播電視|愛爾蘭廣播電視]]的節目《{{tsl|en|Home School Hub|家庭學校中心}}》最後一集中與{{tsl|en|RTÉ Concert Orchestra|愛爾蘭廣播電視管弦樂團}}一同演出<ref>{{Cite news |date=2020-06-17 |title=Allie Sherlock plays graduation gig for Home School Hub |archive-date=2020-06-19 |url=https://www.rte.ie/entertainment/2020/0617/1148117-allie-sherlock-plays-graduation-gig-for-home-school-hub/ |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200619115305/https://www.rte.ie/entertainment/2020/0617/1148117-allie-sherlock-plays-graduation-gig-for-home-school-hub/ |access-date=2020-06-19 }}</ref>。2020年7月，女性藝術家群體「{{tsl|en|Irish Women in Harmony||Irish Women in Harmony}}」錄製〈{{tsl|en|Dreams (The Cranberries song)||Dreams}}〉的新版本支助一個[[家庭暴力|家庭暴力]]慈善機構，而夏洛克是該群體的一員<ref name="it-1">{{cite news |last1=Bol |first1=Rosita |title=Irish Women in Harmony record Cranberries song in aid of Safe Ireland |url=https://www.irishtimes.com/culture/music/irish-women-in-harmony-record-cranberries-song-in-aid-of-safe-ireland-1.4283348 |accessdate=2020-07-03 |publisher=The Irish Times |language=en}}</ref>。

== 個人生活 ==
夏洛克來自[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]]{{tsl|en|Douglas, Cork|道格拉斯 (科克)|道格拉斯}}<ref>{{Cite web |title=12-year-old Douglas girl turns down appearance on The Ellen Show |url=https://www.echolive.ie/corknews/12-year-old-Douglas-girl-turns-down-appearance-on-The-Ellen-Show-d9fff5dc-9e1e-4f27-8f62-bae2dda9fd7e-ds |dead-url=no |website=echolive.ie | publisher = {{tsl|en|The Echo (Cork newspaper)||The Echo}} |archive-date=2020-06-19 |access-date=2020-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200619114332/https://www.echolive.ie/corknews/12-year-old-Douglas-girl-turns-down-appearance-on-The-Ellen-Show-d9fff5dc-9e1e-4f27-8f62-bae2dda9fd7e-ds}}</ref>，出生於2005年4月7日<ref>{{Cite AV media | date=2020-03-20 |title=Allie Sherlock Live show from Home |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fxMzpvFXvto&t=563 |access-date=2020-04-19 |via=YouTube |minutes=9 |quote='When are you turning 15?' 'April 7th.' }}</ref>。夏洛克2016年離開小學，目前[[在家自學|在家自學]]。他的父親馬克·夏洛克（Mark Sherlock）會為她錄製影片並上傳至YouTube頻道<ref name="examiner2018"/>。

